{
  "title": "Buttery Buttery Ukrainian Yogurt Stir-fry",
  "description": "A fluffy and buttery Ukrainian dish featuring soured cream and chive dip in a one-pot recipe that is also paleo-friendly, perfect for a quick breakfast or side.",
  "cuisine": "Ukrainian",
  "diet": [
